reviewText: Stunning DVD, as described. Although now several years old, the hunting footage and relevant commentary is very good. Not filmed in wide screen but can been viewed in wide screen without distortion.

I love duck hunting enough that I can sit and watch it all summer dreaming of the fall events to come.  While I enjoyed this DVD, I am always hoping for something new or different.  This delivers more of the same, fun to watch but easily forgotten and not one I would return to time and time again
